what the hell are you? 

16:45.716 --> 16:49.316
I'll get to know him and then we'll see
who the real samurai is. 

16:49.317 --> 16:51.517
So you know where our man is? 

16:51.518 --> 16:54.518
Yes boss.
I know the hospital and the room. 

16:54.519 --> 17:00.519
